{"tid":787814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港醫思醫療將與企鵝醫生合作在港開設20間全科診所","createTime":"2018-08-21T03:34:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-21T03:45:46.000Z","uid":13468,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9e22332515e8aeca6d7e5fc76340ae50e24dbbac","tid":787814,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T03:34:58.000Z","msg":"香港醫思醫療將與企鵝醫生合作在港開設20間全科診所<br />\n<br />\n21/8/2018 9:23<br />\n        香港醫思醫療(02138)公布, 將會與騰訊(00700)旗下的企鵝醫生組成合資企業, 合作在本港開設全科診所.<br />\n        企鵝醫生將會持有合資企業五成半股權, 香港醫思醫療會持有四成本, 初步計劃總資本投入不少於1000萬元, 目標是開設20間診所, 預計今年底前會開設兩間診所.<br />\n<br />\n        <strong>另外, 雙方亦會共同投資及研發IT系統, 發展境外醫生在境內會診等中港醫療服務.</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/default.aspx?NewsID=20180821092354\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Fdefault.aspx%3FNewsID%3D20180821092354&d=AIB9wnxRt8rjcHg3QClxIf755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=fac5785f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/default.aspx?NewsID=20180821092354</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94cbaf2156eb7fa21b641594f2f8d21d46c31422","tid":787814,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T03:36:19.000Z","msg":"境外可以係先進國家啫&hellip;&hellip;山"},{"pid":"7872a57b5469b549275de1c632ae22254c4f5107","tid":787814,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T03:45:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}